     H            Y.
     F** GCQR87 *******************************************************
     F*  DIE SETTING# INQUIRY ( DIE INFORMATION DATA CREATE - 2 )     *
     F*----------+-----+---------+------------------------------------*
     F*2022.05.12|TEC. |T.MITSUI | 22047  INITIAL VERSION.            *
     F******************************************************* GCQR87 **
     F*          FILE DEFINE                              *
     F*****************************************************
     F*==< DIE INFORMATION DATA (1) >==*
     FGCQWP86 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*
     F*==< SALES TOTALIZATION FILE >==*
     FMBEPL05 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*
     F*==< FORECAST INTRAL PART NO. >==*
     FABMPL21 IF  E           K        DISK
     F*
     F*==< DIE INFORMATION DATA (2) >==*
     FGCQWP87 O   E                    DISK
     F*
     E*****************************************************
     E*          ARRAY DEFINE                             *
     E*****************************************************
     E                    @YYM        6  6 0
     E                    @ISR       12  9 0
     E                    @OSR        6  9 0
     E*
     I*****************************************************
     I*          DATA STRACTURE DEFINE                    *
     I*****************************************************
     I*==< SYSTEM INF. >==*
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM @@PGM
     I                                      244 253 @@WSID
     I                                      254 263 @@USER
     I                                      264 269 @@JBNO
     I*==< GCQWP86 >==*
     I            DS
     I                                        1  93 W1REC@
     I                                        1   2 W1KAT1
     I                                        3   6 W1KAT2
     I                                        7   91W1LTIM
